game.name: Mini Ear Doctor
game.description:
Oh no! Your favorite Minion has a major ear infection and it is getting very difficult for him to bear the pain caused by the severe ear injury. Someone has told him about your medical laboratory where the medial facility for all types of wounds and problems are taken care of. Remember he needs immediate medical attention so try to provide him with the best treatment as fast as you can. Join Mini Ear Doctor and be prepared to cure his ear problem and make him feel better!

This cute little yellow minion relies on your doctoring skills a lot so feel free to implement any medical techniques to get his ear treated in this brand new doctor game. Grab all the tools you see on-screen to help this little creature with his issue! You would have lasers, syringes and a microscope to deal with nasty ear infections. There are many obstacles like germs, dirt, wax and over-grown hair to deal with. Remove those hairs first to get a clear view of his ear.

Give him a proper wax and then start treating the problem with the help of the essential medical tools in this cool surgery game! Make sure to pay attention to the details to turn his ear back to its normal and healthy state. Find the tools at the bottom of the screen. Try to challenge your ultimate doctoring skills to cure his deadly ear infection and make him feel happy again!
